    <summary>A minimalist target runner for C# scripts.</summary>
    <description>A minimalist C# script library for writing targets for building, analysing, testing, packaging, deploying, etc. and running them using any runner which supports the "standard" C# script dialect (as defined by csi.exe).

In no way restricted to writing targets related to .NET projects.

See the quickstart at https://github.com/adamralph/simple-targets-csx#quickstart</description>
